(Translated by Google) Beautiful urban square in memory of the workers who made tin pieces at the old Angus factories. Large piece of metal found on site.

(Original)
Beau square urbain en mémoire des ouvriers qui fabriquaient des pièces en fer-blanc au ancienne usines Angus. Grande pièce de métal retrouvée sur place.

(Translated by Google) Park of my adolescence.

(Original)
Parc de mon adolescence.
